</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 234</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Media and Health Discourses</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Throughout the lessons, these stereotypes of health discourses will be discussed from different perspectives. In the following lessons, students will be asked to choose a text or material to discuss these stereotypes of health discourses.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414376&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 235</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Stres Management in Health Care</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Stress Management in healthcare and prevention and treatment</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414377&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 236</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Modernisation in Turkey</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414399&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 237</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Cultural Artifacts and Social Identity</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course introduces students the various aspects of evaluating cultural artifacts. The course begins with the theoretical background of culture and its relevant vocabulary. The following path covers an array of topics including, but not limited to, economy, political appearance of culture, media, heritage, and myth. The focus on these topics will be accompanied by structural issues such as inequality, social class, and cultural capital.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414385&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 238</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Reading and Walking Istanbul</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The objective of this course is to examine the transformation of the City of Istanbul starting from the Turkish Modernity and trace the urban and social developments during the Istanbul’s gaining a global facet. The course will cover different phases and appearances of the urban history and structure of Istanbul. Right to the City, The Understanding of Locality, Urban Gender Relations, Migration, Development of Infrastructure, Formal and Informal Labor Practices, Public Space and Public Health will be part of the readings and discussions.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414386&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 240</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History, Culture and Society of Turkey through Cinema</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414387&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 241</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Microbiota in Health and Disease</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Bu ders ile temel kavramlardan başlanılarak tedavi uygulamalarına kadar geniş bir bakış açısıyla mikrobiyomun sağlık ve hastalıktaki rolleri farklı disiplinlerden öğrencilere anlatılacaktır. Bu dersin içeriğinde; Mikrobiyomun tanımı, Mikrobiyomun insan vücudunda gelişimi ve dağılımı, Mikrobiyomun insan sağlığı, metabolizması ve hastalıkları ile ilişkisi, Mikrobiyom-ilaç etkileşimleri, Probiyotik ve prebiyotiklerin farmasötik tedavilerdeki yeri ve fekal mikrobiyota transplantasyonu, Mikrobiyomun toplumsal sağlık üzerindeki etkisi, enfeksiyon kontrolü ve antibiyotik direnci yer almaktadır.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414402&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
