<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course provides a basis for the definition of technology, the importance of technology in nursing care applications, the technological products used in patient care applications, the positioning and usage of technological products in the hospital environment, the effect of technology on patient safety.</Data></Cell>
