<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Skin Structure and Physiology, Wound Definition, Wound Care History, Wound Etiology, Wound Classification, Wound Healing Types, Nursing Care in Wound Healing Stages, Wound Evaluation, Wound Complications, Factors Affecting Wound Healing, Wound Care Principles and Patient Safety, Valid in Wound Care Instruments, Pressure Injury and Care, Diabetic Foot and Care, Venous-Arterial Wounds and Care, Evaluation of Evidence-Based Practices for Wound Care (Pressure Injury), Wound Care Products and New Technologies</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414195&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
