<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 310</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Child Health and Diseases Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4+9+4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">10,5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">In the world and in Turkey the situation of children, child health and diseases An overview of nursing, factors affecting the development of children&apos;s health, structure of health services, child rights, child neglect and abuse of children&apos;s growth and development, child and family health monitoring, culturally sensitive assessment and development , immunization, family-centered care, admission of the child to the hospital, pharmacological differences in children, communication with children and families, pain assessment and control in children, atraumatic care, child-specific differences in nursing interventions, care for healthy and high-risk newborns, age periods (baby, play, school pre-school, childhood, adolescent) specific health promotion and family, age-specific health problems and care, system-specific diseases and care in childhood</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414257&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
