<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">It includes related knowledge and skills to the status and history of Home Care Services in Turkey and in the world, the role and responsibilities of Home Care Services team, planning, implementation and evaluation of the maintenance of individuals who need home care</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414224&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRSE 310</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Rehabilitation Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Rehabilitation Nursing Course
General Concepts and Principles of Rehabilitation Nursing
Self-Care in Rehabilitation Patients: Bowel and Bladder Management
Self-Care in Rehabilitation Patients: Improving Cognition, Communication and Behavior
Self-Care for Rehabilitation Patients: Education of Patients and Families
Rehabilitation in Special Cases: Cardiac and Pulmonary Rehabilitation
Rehabilitation in special situations: Rehabilitation in individuals with amputation
Rehabilitation in special situations: traumatic brain injury, Spinal Cord injury
Evaluation
Self-Care in Rehabilitation Patients: Swallowing and Nutritional Status
Gerontological Rehabilitation
Musculoskeletal Injuries in Rehabilitation Nursing
Pediatric Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414321&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRSE 306</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Evidence Based Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to evidence-based nursing, basic concepts in evidence-based practice, sources and use of evidence, application of research evidence, evidence-based nursing care steps, evidence-based practice process.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414259&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 405</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Community Awareness Project</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">04.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">With a sense of social responsibility, they can organize projects and activities for their social environment in collaboration with professional and non-governmental organizations. They can implement project plans.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414323&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 407</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Mental Health and Psychiatric Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4+9+4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">10,5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">06.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">It contributes to the acquisition of nursing knowledge and skills in the protection and development of mental health and care, treatment and rehabilitation in cases where mental health is impaired.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414261&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 409</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Public Health Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4+9+4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">10,5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">04.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">By enabling the training of well-equipped and conscious public health nurses, it provides to gain knowledge, attitude and skills in order to protect and improve the health of individuals living in the community.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414262&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 456</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Surgical Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">In healthcare areas where surgical treatment is applied, the assessment of the physiological, psychological and social needs of the individual during the surgical process contributes to the development of knowledge and skills for effective and safe care practices.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414198&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 458</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Women&apos;s Health and Diseases Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Graduates who complete this course will be able to identify normal and risky pregnancy conditions, provide nursing support during normal labor, deliver appropriate postpartum care, plan and implement nursing interventions for benign and malignant tumors of reproductive organs, and evaluate patient outcomes.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414199&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 460</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Mental Health and Psychiatric Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Contribute to the preservation, development of mental health and the acquisition of nursing knowledge and skills in care, treatment and rehabilitation in cases where mental health is impaired.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414201&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 462</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Principles and Methods in Nursing Education</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">04.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">It helps students to reflect their theoretical knowledge, attitudes and skills on the education of patients and their relatives into practice in the clinic and gain competence; to see and be involved in health education activities planned by the institution; and to observe the orientation and in-service education activities planned in the institution regarding in-service education.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414388&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 464</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Medical Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">04.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">A graduate who takes this course will have
the ability to plan, implement and evaluate patient outcomes in the fields of diabetes and its management,
which are global emergencies; in cardiovascular diseases and cancers that are increasingly widespread in
the world; palliative care in different diseases; intensive care of patients in stroke, chest pain and other
emergencies.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414197&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 466</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Child Health and Diseases Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">04.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Contributes to the development of knowledge, attitudes and skills in protecting and improving the health of children and their families, diagnosing, caring for and evaluating the risky / sick child.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414200&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 468</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Public Health Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">By enabling the training of well-equipped and conscious public health nurses, it provides to gain knowledge, attitude and skills in order to protect and improve the health of individuals living in the community.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414202&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NRS 470</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Management in Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">04.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The nursing management course helps the members of the profession to understand legal and administrative responsibilities in the professional field and to take on roles and responsibilities in management and organizational processes in the units and organizations that provide health care services in which they will work.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414244&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
</Table>
