<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">If this course is successfully completed, students will have knowledge about the history and movements of cinema and will learn to establish a relationship between cinema and philosophy.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=414375&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
