<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">10</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">To detect “what is happening in our body” in various emotional states and to detect negative emotions (sadness, fear, anxiety, jealousy, disgust, hatred...), positive emotions (enthusiasm, interest, satisfaction, calmness, faith, joy...) creative drama essays on increasing one&apos;s status</Data></Cell>
