<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History Of Cinema</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">9</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Hollywood in the 1950’s: The mutual influence of television and film
